Do’s
Use a professional and respectful tone in your posts
Think before you post or share anything
Take care of your privacy by changing your settings
Be sure of the information you share
Use social media for learning, networking, and positive activities
  
Dont's
Do not share your personal or sensitive information
Do not share offensive or inappropriate content
Do not share rumors or false information
Do not get involved in online arguments or negative discussions
Do not use social media for important activities
